Description:
  mws:vlad generator creates required files for Vlad deployments. Features:
   - environment-specific configs (eg. rake vlad:deploy env=<environment>)
   - app_server management with god
   - rock solid rvmrc management in deploy target servers
   - cleans up cached javascripts and stylesheets on deploy
   - runs deploy:after_update task at deploy target servers
   - generates deploy rake tasks (which invokes configuration generator)
   - generates configuration generators (which creates config/unicorn.god)